{"TopicId":143043,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Happy Aphelion!","CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T21:30:22Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T21:30:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTomorrow, July 4th 2016, is Earth\u0027s highest point in its orbit around the Sun! Yay random astronomy facts!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-03T21:31:33Z\u0022 title=\u002207/03/2016 09:31  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by cubinator\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T21:51:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh neat. Because of how time zones work, I am living in this \u0022tomorrow\u0022\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T22:03:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660087\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467582691\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155194\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Atlas2342\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Atlas2342 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh neat. Because of how time zones work, I am living in this \u0022tomorrow\u0022\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s why I specified the date.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T22:10:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, isn\u0027t that fun. It\u0027s summer*, but we\u0027re at the farthest from the Sun. Pretty cool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*almost 90% of humanity lives in the Northern Hemisphere, so it\u0027s summer for most of humanity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-03T22:31:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660115\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467583831\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022127797\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bill Phil\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, Bill Phil said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, isn\u0027t that fun. It\u0027s summer*, but we\u0027re at the farthest from the Sun. Pretty cool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. It also means that perihelion happens really close to New Year. Earth doesn\u0027t really see the effects of its fluctuating altitude because our eccentricity is quite low, but on Mars the summers in the southern hemisphere are a lot warmer than those in the northern hemisphere because those occur during perihelion and its eccentricity is higher than ours. Sometimes it even gets above 0 \u00B0C!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: And sometimes it\u0027s colder where I live than on Mars!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-03T22:32:23Z\u0022 title=\u002207/03/2016 10:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 3, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by cubinator\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HazelPine","CreatedById":164526,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T02:14:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd where I live it\u0027s colder than normal! And during winter! Good thing it never gets lower than 5 degrees though.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T02:17:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy Aphelion Day. It\u0027s all downhill from here!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RainDreamer","CreatedById":129077,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T02:19:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd we just keep on falling, falling down~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T02:23:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660329\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467598659\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy Aphelion Day. It\u0027s all downhill from here!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660332\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467598796\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129077\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RainDreamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, RainDreamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd we just keep on falling, falling down~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, until Perihelion day sometime in early January. Then we\u0027ll be falling up again!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Waxing_Kibbous","CreatedById":151611,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T03:45:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660332\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467598796\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129077\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RainDreamer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, RainDreamer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd we just keep on falling, falling down~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/EyBrFHJ4VSo?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T05:10:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Turns out though, that\u0027s why the Sun looks so small this week...)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMerry Aphelion!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scotius","CreatedById":57622,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T06:21:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill, thanks to the Earth moving slower at Aphelion, summer on the northern hemisphere last several days longer than in the south. Conversely, winter is shorter up here. Yaaay!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T09:13:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI live in the UK where the weather bears no respect for anything, including season, distance from sun or how many sacrificial goats you go through. The Earth could be projected out of Sol System into deep space and in the UK it would still be overcast and damp.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T13:15:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAphelion occurs at 12:24 PM EDT, or 16:24 GMT. Just letting everyone know so you can, uh, I dunno. Jump, maybe?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T13:22:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660829\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467638125\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nso you can, uh, I dunno. Jump, maybe?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTurn prograde and perform an apoapsis burn.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T13:28:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660838\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467638578\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTurn prograde and perform an apoapsis burn.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr save some delta-V on a retrograde burn. Neither planet there is in position for a Hohmann transfer, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T13:36:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo we have the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E needed to circularise?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T14:39:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660854\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467639390\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo we have the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E needed to circularise?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDepends. Are we using the force of jumping, or do we need to all fart prograde at the same time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T14:59:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660900\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467643170\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150330\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cubinator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, cubinator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDepends. Are we using the force of jumping, or do we need to all fart prograde at the same time?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSilly, those won\u0027t work. I propose a global initiative (we still have 6 minutes) to paint an appropriately oriented \u0022go faster stripe\u0022 on their house. The cumulative effect should do the job. If you go deep into the maths, this is exactly how Cannae/EM drives work.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T15:20:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222660936\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022143043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467644350\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSilly, those won\u0027t work. I propose a global initiative (we still have 6 minutes) to paint an appropriately oriented \u0022go faster stripe\u0022 on their house. The cumulative effect should do the job. If you go deep into the maths, this is exactly how Cannae/EM drives work.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe actually have an hour and \u003Cs\u003Esix\u003C/s\u003E three\u00A0minutes. The millions of stripes on the American flags people are toting right now should help, too.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-04T15:21:21Z\u0022 title=\u002207/04/2016 03:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 4, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by cubinator\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-04T15:51:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe should be very careful to keep the Earth rotation untouched.\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo,\u003Cbr\u003E\nthose who currently have 12h (probably America) would turn their... face in one direction,\u003Cbr\u003E\nmidnight\u00A0 (East Asia) - in the opposite direction,\u003Cbr\u003E\nothers - make their burn in radial (from/to the Sun) direction to compensate the angular impulse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}